Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲开 躲开 快跳船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下搞不好要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 刚才那下我家附近炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:00:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带来…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的安宁…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 骏骏 没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去救大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骏骏 师傅他们就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 巴哈姆特那混蛋出现时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应一个女人会保护好她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果我放弃了她的生命选择了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你会选哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去快回 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界会变成啥样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事你根本不需要考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狠狠揍一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我干掉那家伙之后还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条命随你们处置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下 祝你出师大捷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口是心非
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下一到多洛莫斯立刻撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军集中力量防守
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要献上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就陪你一起献上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要跟着送死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是我的生命还是你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死…死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得救啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怪物真的死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我引以为傲的徒弟哦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈可否安好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如今仍在过着王都的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王都因复兴工程变得非常繁忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知你那边没怎么遭受巴哈姆特的危害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倍感安心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必我这辈子都不会忘记那天发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会忘的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为英雄的国王从那天起便失明了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他还在当国王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的 打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 王都的人类跟恶魔之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨消失 和好如初…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不像之前 如今已没有奴隶啥的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许关系正在逐渐改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德离开了王都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说现在住在神界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算回老家之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让奶奶驮着我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔阿萨谢尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴卡斯还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我当成家人 温柔地接纳了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小姑娘 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算赖到啥时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你俩也来帮帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔在那天失去了重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在已经完全振作起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我做了美昧的饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘的话音…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然无法恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想不到代价竟是话音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是喊你们来帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不嫌弃的话 我可以教你怎么做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 代替我给那个醉鬼做如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:16:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴卡斯喜欢索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人怎么可能给这种冒牌神做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁是冒牌神啊 该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别跟着起哄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…别笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会我会向妈妈介绍这些出色的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 我可没做你那份料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我今天不是来喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是时候出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就不喜欢王都这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是回归放浪生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是乎 我明天早上就启程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我给你个拥抱啥的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？见谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在巴哈姆特的光芒中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤往哪边吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到王都之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心的事 快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤得让人想哭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种各样的事发生了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今后还会过得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈姆特根本没死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 阿米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦罗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就能重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢收看

